# APISpikeRadar - Latency Spike and Error Burst Detector

APISpikeRadar identifies and logs sudden latency increases, failures, or availability gaps in APIs.

## Features
- Spike/burst detection  
- Parallel endpoint scans  
- CSV / JSON logs  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_APISpikeRadar.git
cd 30_APISpikeRadar
python monitor.py
